    {
      "_id": "TPh233wZn5b9RYiY",
      "name": "Insidious Mummy Rot",
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/Passive.webp",
      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-traits=\"disease,curse\" data-pf2-label=\"Insidious Mummy Rot DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"26\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em data-visibility=\"gm\">This disease and any damage from it can't be healed until this curse is removed. A creature killed by mummy rot turns to dust and can't be resurrected except by a 7th-level @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.kqhPt9344UkcGVYO]{Resurrect} ritual or similar magic.</em></p>\n<p><em data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Stage 1</strong>, carrier with no ill effect (1 minute) @Item[29AmuCya4JLpmwrT]{Afflicted}</em></p>\n<p><em data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Stage 2</strong>, [[/r 4d6 # negative damage]] negative damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 1} (1 day) @Item[vifV4AaC7MTLXXD1]{Insidious Mummy Rot}</em></p>",
          "chat": "",
          "unidentified": ""
        },
        "source": {
